## Steps of Pipeline

### 1.) Obtain the Raw Data (Genomes & Raw Reads) & mito genome
*Make a single download script 
- if the genomes and raw reads exist in the Data directory,
	echo "Raw data exists and is ready to process"
	continue
- if not, 
	./sra_grab.sh
	./genome_fetch.sh

### 2.) Trim and filter the Reads 
-input data is raw_reads
#### Trim
-fastp default parameters
-index_and_map
	./trim_and_filter.sh
#### Index, Map, & remove Mito
- if index exists for file,
	continue:
- if not, 
	##### index the mito
	bowtie2 index $mito genome

##### map reads to mito index
- bowtie2 map reads to mito genome
##### convert sam to bam and sort
- samtools view -bS
- samtools sort
##### convert bam to fastq
- samtools fastq 

